                     <interp inst="t18261026-103-person711" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am headborough of Mile-end Old-town - I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>BRIGHT'S Defence. We were paid 6d. to wheel them to Whitechapel - we first carried them because it was muddy.</p>
               <p>BRIGHT - <rs id="t18261026-103-verdict566" type="verdictDescription">
